Adds six new blog card component styles
Introduces Aurora background, Bauhaus, Neumorphism, white space, bold typography, and minimalistic design variations to expand the available blog card styling options.
Each style provides distinct visual aesthetics: - Aurora uses animated gradient backgrounds with glassmorphism effects - Bauhaus incorporates geometric shapes with bold colors and typography - Neumorphism creates soft, inset shadow effects for depth - White space emphasizes clean layout with generous spacing - Bold typography features high contrast with strong font weights - Minimalistic offers clean, simple design with subtle interactions
Enhances design flexibility for blog post presentation across different themes and branding requirements.
